{"tid":486093,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人上過麗瑤之家做義工？","createTime":"2017-12-01T13:46:18.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-31T02:27:39.000Z","uid":30259,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"6fdbf4aeb8d092513771b62c2e1f424de641bbaf","tid":486093,"uid":30259,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-01T13:46:18.000Z","msg":"好想幫助下D社會有需要人士<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n麗瑤之家在1997年成立，家舍秉持以人為本的服務理念，與各持份者緊密協作，為50位15歲或以上的嚴重殘疾人士提供一個全面照顧及舒適安全的生活環境； 並透過多樣化的生活體驗，提升服務使用者的生活質素。在2004年12月家舍增設『天倫居』親子渡假式服務，讓殘疾人士和家人能在家舍職員的支援下渡宿共 聚天倫。<br />\n<br />\n地址：新界葵涌麗瑤邨商場大廈二零四室<br />\n電話：<br />\n2742-1112<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.fuhong.org/fuhong_mobile/PageInfo.aspx?md=20000&amp;cid=281\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.fuhong.org%2Ffuhong_mobile%2FPageInfo.aspx%3Fmd%3D20000%26cid%3D281&d=tNwcjnXSWuSGrbc4ibZRkGi1w7%2FDyS2Kz%2BsYtkalU0Y%3D&h=5f52b7b6\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.fuhong.org/fuhong_mobile/PageInfo.aspx?md=20000&amp;cid=281</a>"},{"pid":"f4dbb09ea22ba9d0acb8eaf0e9c9852a9b01bb97","tid":486093,"uid":30259,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-01T13:48:55.000Z","msg":"社會有需要人士係好需要大家嘅愛同關心<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4d5370b19c2c4986d62d6696872571ba0ae7ba82","tid":486093,"uid":30259,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-01T13:51:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a44f8de3a5a8c89590b34a484f32513d5af17ccc","tid":486093,"uid":22858,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-01T14:02:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://1.bp.blogspot.com/-ZgXLysvzBv8/UJpcUjLy6uI/AAAAAAAAAcs/_KN4eCwYtos/s1600/hkflagIl759.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2F1.bp.blogspot.com%2F-ZgXLysvzBv8%2FUJpcUjLy6uI%2FAAAAAAAAAcs%2F_KN4eCwYtos%2Fs1600%2FhkflagIl759.gif&h=88ac342b&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"ht